                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Hold at the fence, resident. This is a managed agricultural asset. Foot traffic through standing yield constitutes unlicensed commerce, and unlicensed commerce constitutes a conversation with me."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The family that used to run this parcel has been transitioned. The crop belongs to the Company now, and the Company does not do trespass. It does engagements. Would you like one?"
                        }
                    ],
